This folder contains the codes for scan of selection and discovery of candidate genes

Cal_hapflk.sh
Cal_Pai.sh
Cal_rehh.R

These three script calculate hapFLK, nucleotide diversity and XP-EHh respectively
_______________________________________________________________________________

Plot_hapFLK.R
Plot_pai.R
Plot_rehh.R

These three R codes process and visualize the results produced above.
_______________________________________________________________________________

Cluster_SNP.R

This script cluster significant SNP into regions
_______________________________________________________________________________

Find_cand_gene.sh 
Plot_cand.R
Plot_cand_fun.R

These three files search for candidate genes in the candidate regions, 
and visualize statistics and genotypes within the candidate regions
First, Find_cand_gene.sh find genes in the candidate regions and fetch the statistics of the candidate genes
Second, Find_cand_gene.sh call Plot_cand.R to get detailed information for these genes and plot statistics
Plot_cand_fun.R contains the functions Plot_cand.R needs, Plot_cand.R will load Plot_cand_fun.R in the process.


